#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/spring-web.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "⚠️ Important: These types are only available when using the Classic RESTEasy stack (quarkus-resteasy / quarkus-resteasy-jackson) because they rely on the Servlet API provided by Undertow (quarkus-undertow)."
